This command will list all the language packs available:

lynx -dump http://www.koffice.org/releases/$pkgver-release.php|grep bz2$|sed 's/.*n-\(.*\)-[0-9].*/\1/'|grep -v bz2

This command was used in a small fix:
for i in koffice-i18n-*
do
	cd $i
	sed -i 's%install || return 1%install || return 1\n\trm $startdir/pkg/opt/kde/share/locale/$lang/LC_MESSAGES/kdgantt.mo%' FrugalBuild
	cd ..
done
